Class 5

Handling Checkboxes and RadioButtons:

1. if you only have one checkbox or radiobutton-- you can simply click on it
2. if you have multiple checkboxes or radiobuttons- store them in a list and loop throughout each element

Dropdowns
Dropdown is a menu which allows us to select one or multiple options

        Types of Dropdowns:
            1. Single Select
            2.Multiple Select

            Handling Dropdowns:
                1. click on the dropdown click on the option
                2. using Select class:
                    *In order to use select class we need to make sure we have
                    a <select> tag in html

            Selecting options from dropdown can be done in  3 ways:
            1. by index
            2. by visible text
            2. by value

            In order to deselect options from dropdown we can use the following methods:
            Your DD must be multiple select
            deselectByIndex()
            deselectByValue()
            deselectByVisibleText()
            deselectAll()

